{"tid":1300874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得唔好過份強調寶礦力","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:44:36.000Z","uid":265197,"like":53,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f11b19ede1e27a79aa042050cfe5d39f960add4","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"又話寶礦力盾又寶礦力衫<br />\n<br />\n人地商業決定<br />\n可能主要因素之一係考慮tvb比人杯葛賣廣告效益唔高<br />\n生意佬最怕咩?最怕<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩</span></span><br />\n本身自己曉走上左軌道嘅貨由佢自然落去無事無幹就最好<br />\n<br />\n一間因為咁令佢有咩麻煩<br />\n影響<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生意</span></span><br />\n仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有手尾跟</span></span><br />\n一定係諗你班仆街我暗中支持仲拖我落水<br />\n反而仲有反效果<br />\n到時仲有邊個敢撐我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b096e4371318b43de6c85d9944522b4a332dafa","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9dd06072a2007f43694ae559d2fec4383c144aa8","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3731da9c02b02d17a2e04e7b01e9f5c2dbb0008","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"瘋狂掃佢貨都係支持嘅一種，但去到直接整裝備著上身就太過份"},{"pid":"85ad077e8a0df13bfd93290d43d7133d0100e1b4","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41a37afdffed5befe74d313fbd93e87212a8c462","tid":1300874,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6298e2a6de346023003957b1ab06bc3170b01616","tid":1300874,"uid":273791,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"瘋狂買佢就得㗎啦， 發夢嗰陣時候唔好用佢唻做代表， 擺佢哋上枱都唔會有好結果"},{"pid"